<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空领着和尚们去见唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们把刚才说的全都告诉了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是太可恶了。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一定会帮助你们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天早上，我会去对付虎力大仙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们知道附近有个空的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们领着唐僧他们去了那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上，他们就在那里睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，悟空很早就醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人来敲门。外面传来了一个很大的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是虎力大仙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧突然睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和所有其他和尚一样，都害怕得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净和八戒拿起了兵器。悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家别担心。我会对付这个恶人的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走到了外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”虎力大仙大声问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就因为你有一点点法力，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你就认为你可以欺负那些和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你不觉得丢人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一点点法力？”虎力大仙生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是非常厉害的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“你可没有我厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道吗？玉帝都怕我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我曾经打败过所有天兵天将。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙挺起了胸膛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以求雨。”他说，“你应该不会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也可以啊。这太简单了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那好，我们比一比。”虎力大仙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁求来的雨多，谁就赢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你赢了，我就放了你和所有的和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我赢了，你必须留在这里做我的奴隶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“傻瓜。”悟空说，“我接受你的挑战。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙和所有人进了村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村子中心有一个道家法坛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>法坛上摆着石碑、香，还有写着咒语的符咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多人围了过来，想看看发生了什么事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先来。”虎力大仙说。他走上了法坛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧摇摇头。“这太可怕了。”他咕哝道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看了他一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，师父。悟空会赢的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他赢不了呢？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得留下做奴隶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们永远都不能到达西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真经也永远到不了大唐。”唐僧捂住了脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒说得对，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净说，“我们不用担心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空微笑着站在他们身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙站在法坛上说道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在要向上天求雨了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙点了香，然后坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闭上了眼睛，开始念咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，他烧了一张符咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一张烧完了，他又烧了一张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，所有符咒都烧完了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙举起了石碑，把它摔碎了。砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围的人们都很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抬头看着天空。天开始变暗了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大风刮起，乌云密布，雷声阵阵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧抖了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！他成功了！要下雨了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空咯咯地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都在这儿等着。我马上回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空快速念了个咒语，灵魂离开了身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在天上，悟空看到了风婆婆在扇云。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>东海龙王也来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大叫：“你们都停手！不要下雨了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>